# ======================
# XavLink Mobile Environment Configuration
# ======================

# ======================
# Backend API URL
# ======================
# IMPORTANT: This is OPTIONAL - the app auto-detects the API URL
# 
# Auto-detection priority:
# 1. EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL (if set)
# 2. Expo dev server host + :5000/api (LAN access)
# 3. Android emulator: http://10.0.2.2:5000/api
# 4. iOS simulator: http://localhost:5000/api
#
# Only set this if:
# - Using ngrok tunnel for cross-network testing
# - Using production backend
# - Need to override auto-detection
#
# Examples:
# Development (ngrok): EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://abc123.ngrok.io/api
# Production: EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com/api
# LAN IP: EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:5000/api
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=

# ======================
# ngrok URL (if using ngrok)
# ======================
# EXPO_PUBLIC_NGROK_URL=https://abc123.ngrok.io
